<br>
If you have no chance at getting 10k hp, or 2k AC, dont set those as goals. In fact dont set any goals at all.<br>
<br>
From limited initial parsings, each 100 displayed AC = 4% mitigation improvement.  So each 1 AC = 0.04% mitigation.  If your at 7500 buffed HP lets say, then 0.04% mitigation = 0.0004(7500) = 3 HP. So 1 displayed AC = 3hp equivalence.  Since raw AC on items is multiplied by 1.6 to get displayed AC, then on gear for a 7500 HP buffed warrior, 1 raw AC = about 5 HP.<br>
<br>
7500 hp warrior 1 raw AC = 5 hp<br>
9000 hp warrior 1 raw AC = 6 hp.<br>
<br>
So if your rating say dagarns belt vs bile etched choker:<br>
<br>
Dagarns is 27AC 75 hp, converting to all AC thats 27 + 75/6 = 39.5 equivalent AC<br>
<br>
Bile is 10 AC 100 hp, converting to all AC thats 10 + 100/6 = 26.6 equivalent AC<br>
<br>
The choice between the two is pretty clear to me <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Thats how I rate gear and pick and choose. And dont worry about setting goals for gear, just use what you have at your disposal to the best of yoru ability and you will be happy. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=solinarinnoruuk>Solinar Innoruuk</A> at: 1/29/03 7:32:14 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=azlanaicelander>Azlana Icelander</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sexies Warlady in all o'Norrath</BR>     ...an da moon too!</BR>Steel Warrior Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 544<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/29/03 8:47:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4933.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.ringofshadows.org/images/Azlana7.jpg width=96 height=150></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: AC/HP  and anudder blond roots question</span><hr size=1> eek got headache now *laughs*<br>
